[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1049","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1049.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1333","title":"Red Hat Linux ncftp FTP客户端自动下载选项远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Red Hat Linux 5.0 及之前版本中 ncftp 2.4.2 FTP 客户端的自动下载选项存在命令注入漏洞。远程攻击者可通过在待下载文件名中嵌入 shell 元字符（如 ;、|、` 等），诱使目标用户连接恶意 FTP 服务器并触发自动下载功能，导致任意命令以用户权限执行。该漏洞影响广泛部署的 ncftp 客户端，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1333"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 ncftp 至 3.0.0 及以上版本，该版本已修复自动下载时文件名中 shell 元字符的过滤问题。如无法升级，可在 ncftp 配置中禁用自动下载选项（auto-download），或避免使用 ncftp -a 自动下载模式，手动确认每个文件后再保存。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=89042322924057&w=2","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7240.php","http://www.osvdb.org/6111","http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/rh50-errata-general.html#ncftp"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1049.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1048","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1048.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1332","title":"GNU gzexe临时文件漏洞","description":"Red Hat Linux 5.0及更早版本中gzip软件包的gzexe程序存在符号链接攻击漏洞，本地用户可利用临时文件覆盖其他用户文件，导致文件完整性受损。","severity":"LOW","score":2.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1332"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级gzip软件包至修复版本，或使用mktemp等安全方式创建临时文件；Debian用户可参考DSA-308安装安全更新，Red Hat用户应安装对应补丁。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T11:50:57.730499565+00:00","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=88603844115233&w=2","http://www.debian.org/security/2003/dsa-308","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7241.php","http://www.osvdb.org/3812","http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/rh50-errata-general.html#gzip","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/7845"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1048.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1048.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1046","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1046.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1330","title":"Sleepycat db库 snprintf 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"db库（版本1.85.4）中的snprintf函数忽略了size参数，导致在使用该函数时无法正确限制缓冲区大小。攻击者可利用此漏洞触发缓冲区溢出，造成信息泄露、权限提升或拒绝服务等危害。攻击者需要本地访问权限，且攻击复杂度较低。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1330"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"建议升级db库至1.85.4之后的版本，或应用Red Hat提供的RH42 errata补丁。对于使用db库的应用程序，应避免使用存在缺陷的snprintf实现，改用正确检查size参数的snprintf实现。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T11:35:31.598835092+00:00","references":["http://lists.openresources.com/Debian/debian-bugs-closed/msg00581.html","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602661419259&w=2","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7244.php","http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/rh42-errata-general.html#db"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1046.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1044","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1044.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1328","title":"Red Hat Linux linuxconf 符号链接攻击漏洞","description":"Red Hat Linux 5.1 系统中 linuxconf 工具在 1.11.r11-rh3 之前版本存在安全漏洞，本地用户可通过符号链接攻击（symlink attack）覆盖任意系统文件，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞利用条件为拥有本地账户，攻击复杂度低，无需认证即可完全控制目标系统。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1328"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31","updated":"2026-07-16","remediation":"升级 linuxconf 至 1.11.r11-rh3 或更高版本，该版本修复了符号链接竞争条件问题。Red Hat 官方已发布 RH51 安全公告提供更新包，建议用户通过 Red Hat 官方渠道获取并安装补丁。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T11:21:58.102130741+00:00","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90383955231511&w=2","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7232.php","http://www.osvdb.org/6068","http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/rh51-errata-general.html#linuxconf"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1044.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0847","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0847.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1004","title":"Symantec Norton AntiVirus 恶意文件处理缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Symantec Norton AntiVirus 在解析特制构造的恶意文件（如特定格式的压缩包或文档）时，由于未对输入数据长度进行充分边界校验，存在堆/栈缓冲区溢出缺陷。攻击者在无需认证的情况下，可通过诱导用户扫描或打开恶意文件触发该漏洞，导致杀毒引擎崩溃或执行任意代码，从而绕过安全防护并危害系统安全。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1004"],"sources":["cve","epss"],"published":"1999-12-31","updated":"2026-07-19","remediation":"升级至 Symantec 官方发布的 Norton AntiVirus 修复版本（建议 2000 年及以后的安全更新版本），并及时更新病毒定义库；在补丁就绪前避免扫描来源不明的文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T10:01:26.073385930+00:00","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-1004","https://www.securityfocus.com/bid/893"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0847.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0006","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0006.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0154","title":"Microsoft IIS 2.0/3.0 附加点号源码泄露漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 2.0/3.0 存在源代码泄露漏洞，远程攻击者通过在 ASP 页面 URL 末尾附加一个点号（.），即可绕过服务器脚本执行机制，直接读取 ASP 文件的原始源代码，导致数据库连接字符串、业务逻辑等敏感信息暴露。该漏洞影响 IIS 2.0 及 3.0 版本，攻击无需认证，仅需发送特制 HTTP 请求即可触发，利用难度极低。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0154"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31","updated":"1999-12-31","remediation":"立即升级至 IIS 4.0 或更高版本（可通过 Windows NT 4.0 Option Pack 安装），该漏洞已在 IIS 4.0 及之后版本中修复。对于已停止支持的旧系统，应迁移至受支持的 Windows Server 版本并部署最新安全更新，同时在 IIS 中禁用不必要的脚本映射作为纵深防御。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0154","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20481","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0154.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/269e5b2b6ea60fdb4a03411be38d3e381b26e4c4/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0154.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0154","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0154.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0154.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0154.md","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/acunetix/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0154.yaml","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0154.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x81000/80405/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0006.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0006.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0006.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0002","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0002.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0001","title":"FreeBSD/OpenBSD TCP/IP 实现拒绝服务漏洞","description":"BSD 衍生系统（包括 FreeBSD、OpenBSD 等）的 TCP/IP 协议栈实现中的 ip_input.c 文件存在输入验证漏洞（CWE-20），未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的网络数据包触发该漏洞，导致目标系统崩溃或挂起，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响多个 BSD 衍生操作系统，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0001"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-12-30T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:13.977","remediation":"立即将 FreeBSD 升级至 2.2.8 及以上版本，或将 OpenBSD 升级至 2.3 及以上版本；对于无法升级的系统，下载并安装对应厂商发布的 ip_input.c 补丁。临时缓解措施：在网络边界防火墙或路由器上配置 ACL，丢弃入站 IP 分片包（若业务不需要分片功能），或部署支持 IP 分片校验的入侵防御系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.openbsd.org/errata23.html#tcpfix","http://www.osvdb.org/5707","https://github.com/MarcusGutierrez/complex-vulnerabilities"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0002.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0001","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0001.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0001","title":"FreeBSD/OpenBSD TCP/IP 远程拒绝服务漏洞","description":"FreeBSD 及 OpenBSD 等 BSD 衍生系统 TCP/IP 协议栈实现中的 ip_input.c 文件存在输入验证不当漏洞（CWE-20），远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标系统发送特制的网络数据包触发该漏洞，导致目标系统内核崩溃或死锁，进而造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 FreeBSD、OpenBSD 等多个 BSD 衍生操作系统，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。建议升级至修复版本或应用厂商发布的安全补丁。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0001"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-12-30T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:13.977","remediation":"升级 FreeBSD 至 2.2.8 或 3.0 及以上版本，OpenBSD 升级至 2.4 及以上版本。临时缓解措施可在边界防火墙上过滤畸形 IP 分片包，或禁用不必要的 raw socket 处理功能。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.openbsd.org/errata23.html#tcpfix","http://www.osvdb.org/5707","https://github.com/MarcusGutierrez/complex-vulnerabilities"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0001.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-2006","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-2006.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1573","title":"HP-UX r-cmnds 远程命令服务权限提升漏洞","description":"HP-UX 10.00 至 11.00 系统中，r-cmnds 工具集包含的多个远程命令服务与客户端程序（remshd、rexecd、rlogind、rlogin、remsh、rcp、rexec、rdist）存在多处未知安全漏洞。远程或本地攻击者在具备一定访问条件时，可利用这些漏洞绕过正常的权限校验机制，非法提升自身权限或越权访问系统上的敏感文件，危害系统机密性与完整性。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1573"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-28","updated":"2026-07-17","remediation":"安装 HP 官方发布的安全补丁 PHNE_20835 或更高版本以修复 remshd/rexecd/rlogind 等 r-cmnds 组件漏洞；如无法立即打补丁，应在 /etc/inetd.conf 中注释掉 shell、login、exec 等服务后执行 /sbin/init.d/inetd stop 与 start 重启 inetd，并使用 TCP Wrappers 限制来源 IP 作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.auscert.org.au/render.html?it=490","http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-022.shtml","http://www.kb.cert.org/vuls/id/13217","http://www.securityfocus.com/advisories/1471","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/7860","https://oval.cisecurity.org/repository/search/definition/oval%3Aorg.mitre.oval%3Adef%3A5550"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-2006.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0200","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0200.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0477","title":"Allaire ColdFusion 应用服务器远程文件上传漏洞","description":"ColdFusion Application Server 的表达式求值器（Expression Evaluator）存在访问控制缺陷，远程攻击者可通过 openfile.cfm 脚本绕过权限限制，向目标服务器上传任意文件，进而实现远程文件显示、删除、上传与执行。该漏洞影响 Allaire ColdFusion Server 4.0 及更早版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，且利用代码已公开，实际威胁较大。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0477"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-12-25T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:28.877","remediation":"升级至 Allaire ColdFusion Server 4.0.1 或更高版本，该版本已修复 openfile.cfm 的权限验证缺陷。如无法升级，在 Web 服务器（IIS/Apache）层面限制对 openfile.cfm 的访问，仅允许受信 IP 或移除该文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/115","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19093"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0200.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0200.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0200.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0198","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0198.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0455","title":"Allaire ColdFusion 表达式评估器任意文件读取删除漏洞","description":"ColdFusion 服务器自带的 Expression Evaluator 示例应用（exprcalc.cfm）存在未授权访问漏洞。由于该示例页面未对访问权限进行适当限制，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可直接访问该页面，利用表达式评估功能读取或删除服务器上的任意文件。该漏洞影响 Adobe ColdFusion 多个版本，攻击者仅需知道目标服务器地址即可实施攻击，危害较大。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0455"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-12-25T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:26.050","remediation":"删除 ColdFusion 服务器 webroot 下的 `CFIDE/exprcalc.cfm` 及整个示例应用目录，或升级到不受影响的 ColdFusion 版本（4.0 以上）。生产环境应移除所有示例应用文件，并通过 Web 服务器配置限制对 `/CFIDE/` 目录的访问。如无法立即修复，可在防火墙或 WAF 层面拦截对 `exprcalc.cfm` 的请求作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/115","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1231f6f5f21cc87f3264c90adadd01cbb12e76ba/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0455.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0455","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0455.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/77fd3cf167afc5c82646a191836bcd2f9e51b459/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0455.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/18de81c56daca1c9e33223f0b95bdb8312a1ca75/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-68jc-r2qv-937x/GHSA-68jc-r2qv-937x.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/web-coldfusion.rules","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0455.json","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/ColdFusion.nasl","https://github.com/jdkoftinoff/mb-linux-msli/blob/8adb103e34af9ff1d8d122e9ee2a1808836f0a14/uClinux-dist/user/snort/drop-rules/sid-msg.map"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0198.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0687","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0687.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0892","title":"Netscape Communicator 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Netscape Communicator 4.7 之前版本在处理动态字体时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。当字体长度字段值小于实际字体大小时，程序未能正确验证字体数据长度，导致堆或栈缓冲区溢出。远程攻击者可通过构造特制的动态字体文件，诱使用户在受影响浏览器中打开恶意网页触发该漏洞，可能导致拒绝服务或任意代码执行。该漏洞影响 Netscape Communicator 4.7 之前的所有版本，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0892"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-12-24T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:16.440","remediation":"建议立即升级 Netscape Communicator 至 4.7 或更高版本（如 Netscape 6.x/7.x 或 Mozilla Suite）。若无法立即升级，可在浏览器设置中禁用动态字体下载功能（Edit → Preferences → Fonts → 取消勾选 \"Allow documents to use other fonts\"），或通过防火墙/代理层面拦截 .pfr/.eot 字体文件下载作为临时缓解措施。建议尽快迁移至现代浏览器（Firefox/Chrome/Edge）彻底规避该漏洞。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0892","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/cf29b986be3ae7c9144123b101d864868676099e/1999/CVE-1999-0892.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/8d0ba8eaeba3ff3558e6044a19d5b454dcc12f33/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0892.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0892","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/512c773c61886081b2589de76a8cfde795349819/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0892.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0892.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/3c5965e4a3ad0d0b437f880f71224c9e3d8d5fd5/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3jvw-9ph4-qc53/GHSA-3jvw-9ph4-qc53.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0892.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0687.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0949","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0949.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1109","title":"Eric Allman Sendmail ETRN 命令拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Eric Allman Sendmail 8.10.0 及之前版本存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标 SMTP 服务器发送一系列 ETRN 命令后立即断开连接，而 Sendmail 在连接已终止后仍持续处理这些命令，导致服务器资源被大量消耗，最终造成拒绝服务。该漏洞利用条件简单，无需认证即可触发。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1109"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-12-22T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:44.347","remediation":"升级 Sendmail 至 8.10.0 或更高版本，该版本修复了 ETRN 命令在连接断开后继续处理导致的资源耗尽问题。如无法立即升级，可在 SMTP 服务配置中禁用 ETRN 命令（在 sendmail.cf 中移除或注释 ETRN 相关规则），或通过防火墙限制 SMTP 端口的来源 IP 以减少外部攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94632241202626&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94780566911948&w=2","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7760.php","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/904","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19701","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e25ede9c3545efaa8ff0b393e30e48edb07502a8/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1109.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1109","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1109.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/c1321b1a6b0cb3a4c18f791e2c8443742c0cb0b0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1109.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-jw39-vxm9-j3xr/GHSA-jw39-vxm9-j3xr.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/S/sendmail_etrn_dos.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1109.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_2.list.dict","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0949.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0919","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0919.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1066","title":"id Software Quake 1 服务器 UDP 反射放大漏洞","description":"Quake 1 游戏服务器在处理初始 UDP 游戏连接请求时，会以大量流量数据包进行回应，存在流量放大攻击漏洞。远程攻击者通过伪造源 IP 地址发送特制的 UDP 连接请求，可诱使服务器向目标主机发送大量响应数据，从而实现类似 Smurf 攻击的分布式拒绝服务放大效果。该漏洞影响 Quake 1 服务器软件，CVSS 评分 5.0，攻击者无需认证即可利用，被放大后的流量可耗尽目标带宽资源。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1066"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-12-22T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:38.163","remediation":"建议升级至 QuakeWorld 或 FTE QuakeWorld 等现代引擎版本，其已修复放大攻击漏洞。若无法升级，在网络边界配置入向 ACL 过滤伪造源 IP 的数据包（BCP 38），并对 UDP 26000 端口实施速率限制以缓解攻击影响。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94589559631535&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/7481e97cf7b60a5b982d99d7dad1ea61174940fb/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1066.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1066","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1066.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/c1321b1a6b0cb3a4c18f791e2c8443742c0cb0b0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1066.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-x4qc-6r3x-7rp4/GHSA-x4qc-6r3x-7rp4.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1066.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cwe_details/cwe_details_100_200.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000954.txt","https://github.com/CyberSecAI/CWE-Expert/blob/f634e911e6c24a1ad8b9619383e2ab3eb2d9ebd4/CWE_corpus/markdown/4_cwe_trimmed_top25.md.txt","https://github.com/ws-researcher/CAEA/blob/098ddb07c83845feda3d1b1d56ef634927954af4/KGA/dataSet/ICNS/entN_ids_1"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0919.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1682","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1682.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0997","title":"Washington University WU-FTPD FTP服务器 FTP转换命令执行漏洞","description":"WU-FTPD 2.4.2/2.5.0/2.6.0/2.6.1/2.6.2 版本中启用 FTP 转换功能时存在命令注入漏洞。攻击者通过上传或请求包含精心构造参数的文件名（如包含 shell 元字符或命令参数的文件名），利用转换程序（如 tar、uncompress 等）将文件名作为命令参数解释执行，从而在服务器上执行任意命令。该漏洞影响启用了 FTP conversion 功能的 WU-FTPD 服务器，CVSS 评分 7.5（高危），攻击者需具备 FTP 访问权限且服务器启用了文件转换功能才可利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0997"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-12-20T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:29.343","remediation":"升级到 WU-FTPD 2.6.2 或更高版本，该版本已在 ftpconversions 配置中为 tar 命令添加 \"--\" 参数，阻止以\"-\"开头的畸形文件名被解释为命令选项。如无法升级，应在 ftpaccess 配置文件中禁用 FTP conversion 功能，或迁移至 ProFTPD、vsftpd 等仍在积极维护的 FTP 服务器以消除风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.debian.org/security/2003/dsa-377","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20563","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/bf63c766a0e51c24a528a42a3e26e4fdf58db9e8/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0997.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0997","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-0997.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/08f8d33c39c79a3a93a8b5c441facde3f9e3cc7d/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0997.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f43f79d7ee652229af6058b1c98133bb5bbc17fb/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-2hff-p384-25wq/GHSA-2hff-p384-25wq.json","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/pre2008/wu_ftpd_site_exec.nasl","https://github.com/jdkoftinoff/mb-linux-msli/blob/8adb103e34af9ff1d8d122e9ee2a1808836f0a14/uClinux-dist/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/debian_DSA-377.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0997.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/magicsword-io/Magic-SigExplorer/blob/2c28b91b003429a144a687199ee99ebd26f1a343/Magic-SigExplorer/docs/cve_report.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1682.toml"}]